elements.title: Faith and Confidence
elements.contents: ... that even though Faith and Confidence (pictured) by William C. Beall won the 1958 Pulitzer Prize for photography, the jurors who selected it were unimpressed by all of the entries?

elements.title: Ryokuoushoku Shakai
